replies.bodyText:
Would it not be better to create 2 functions? - one to get 2 char lang code and values like the following
    {
       "en": "English Version (en)",
       "fr": "French Version (fr)"
    }


and one to get 3 char lang codes and values like the following
   {
      "eng": "English Version (en)",
      "fre": "French Version (fr)"
   }


With 2 function, if in the future you want to know where 2 char codes are used vs 3 char code it will be easier to identify usage. This can probably be done by making the main function private and creating 2 public functions that could just subset the existing results.

